[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0862","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0862.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0589","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9108,\"outputTokens\":19,\"totalTokens\":10791}}","description":"Windows NT 系统存在注册表权限配置不当的安全漏洞。系统中某关键注册表项的访问控制列表（ACL）配置错误，导致未经身份认证的远程攻击者可能通过多种方式（如空会话连接、SMB 协议等）获取对该注册表项的写入或修改权限。攻击者可利用此漏洞篡改系统级配置信息，进而提升自身权限、禁用安全服务或进行其他恶意操作，完全绕过原有的访问控制机制。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及早期基于 Windows NT 内核的系统，CVSS 评分高达 10.0，危害等级为严重。建议管理员立即使用注册表编辑器（regedt32）检查并修复相关注册表项的权限配置，严格限制可访问该关键注册表项的用户和组，仅赋予系统管理员必要的读取权限，避免授予写入或完全控制权限。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0589"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:41.410","remediation":"Windows NT 已停止支持，建议立即升级至 Windows Server 2019/2022 或更高版本。若无法升级，使用 regedt32 检查并收紧关键注册表项（如 HKLM\\SAM、HKLM\\SECURITY、HKLM\\SYSTEM）的权限，移除 Everyone 和 Users 组的完全控制权，仅保留 SYSTEM 和 Administrators 的完全控制权。应用 Microsoft 安全配置工具（SCE）或自定义安全模板（.inf）批量修复注册表 ACL。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0589","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0589.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/35cd604fbbf2927fb6acbcd700e81d36cd6dec11/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0589.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0589","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/3a7f9488e77673498ec37285be0a165ad71720f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0589.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0589.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2a2be81fd4b47dc35d815a995b6429bd116a3b84/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2h9f-vc99-85c4/GHSA-2h9f-vc99-85c4.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/smb_reg_hklm.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0589.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/S/smb_reg_schedule.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0862.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0859","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0859.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0587","title":"开源应用 WWW 服务器文件系统信息泄露漏洞","description":"该漏洞源于 OpenSource Application 的 WWW 服务器未能在受限制的文件系统中运行（如未使用 chroot 实现）。攻击者无需身份验证即可直接访问服务器的文件系统，这导致攻击者能够浏览和获取系统内所有关键文件和敏感信息，如配置文件、密码数据库、账号凭证等。受影响系统涵盖各种运行 OpenSource Application 的 Web 服务器，由于此类服务器广泛应用于众多企业和机构，因此整体影响范围极大。攻击者仅需向目标服务器发送简单 HTTP 请求即可触发漏洞，操作简单且风险较低，适合大规模扫描利用。攻击者通过获取系统关键文件，可进一步获取权限提升、利用其他漏洞、破坏系统完整性等高级恶意行为。该漏洞因其极端危害性获得 CVSS 满分 10.0 分，被列为严重安全事件，亟需系统重新构建安全沙箱环境，确保 Web 服务隔离和文件系统安全控制。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0587"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:41.170","remediation":"将Web服务器进程限制在chroot jail或容器环境中运行，配置DocumentRoot限制文档根目录，禁用FollowSymLinks选项防止目录遍历，以最小权限用户（如www-data）运行Web服务进程，禁用不必要的模块（如mod_autoindex），配置open_basedir限制PHP脚本访问路径，部署WAF规则阻断目录遍历攻击Payload（如../等），定期审计Web目录权限确保最小权限原则。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0587","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/35cd604fbbf2927fb6acbcd700e81d36cd6dec11/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0587.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0587","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0587.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/3a7f9488e77673498ec37285be0a165ad71720f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0587.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2a2be81fd4b47dc35d815a995b6429bd116a3b84/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-w7xx-5rj3-rrrc/GHSA-w7xx-5rj3-rrrc.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0587.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86250/info.html","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000443.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--eccf97d2-38b3-43a5-bc13-280cb22967b1.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0859.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0848","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0848.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0581","title":"微软 Windows NT 注册表 HKEY_CLASSES_ROOT 权限配置不当漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统的 HKEY_CLASSES_ROOT 注册表根键被配置了不恰当的、涉及系统关键的访问权限。该注册表项存放着文件类型关联、COM 组件及 OLE 对象等关键系统配置，正常应仅允许管理员修改。由于权限设置过于宽松，本地已登录的普通用户或低权限用户可对该项及其子项进行写入、修改甚至删除操作。攻击者在具备本地登录权限的条件下，可通过 regedit 等工具或调用注册表 API 篡改关联的程序路径或 COM 对象，进而实现权限提升、持久化驻留或破坏系统稳定性，影响所有受此错误权限配置影响的 Windows NT 系统。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0581"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:40.473","remediation":"重置 HKEY_CLASSES_ROOT 注册表项的访问控制列表为默认权限：仅 Administrators 组和 SYSTEM 账户拥有完全控制权限，Users 组和 Everyone 仅保留读取权限。可使用 regini.exe 工具通过注册表配置文件批量修复，命令为：regini fix_hkcr_perms.txt，其中配置文件内容为 \\HKEY_CLASSES_ROOT 1 [administrators 全控] [system 全控] [users 读取] [everyone 读取]。若无法立即修复，可将注册表项权限导出备份后通过 regedit 手动修改，并在防火墙和组策略中限制对注册表的远程访问。建议升级到受支持的 Windows 版本以彻底消除此漏洞。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0581","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0581.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/770e8f09ce14e637a09c7c619e10772aa6172bea/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0581.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0581","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/e1298ff7aafe81b936ca67ecef34c3124d6c72f0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0581.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0581.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2a2be81fd4b47dc35d815a995b6429bd116a3b84/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3rwh-j2p9-wp9q/GHSA-3rwh-j2p9-wp9q.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0581.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86236/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0848.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0845","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0845.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0579","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 注册表审核策略日志记录缺失漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统的注册表审核策略存在缺陷，对非关键注册表键值的访问操作（无论成功或失败）均不会记录审核事件日志。攻击者可利用此缺陷在不留下审计痕迹的情况下修改非关键注册表键值，潜在地篡改系统配置或植入恶意配置，从而规避安全审计机制的检测。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 系列操作系统，CVSS 评分 10.0，属于严重级别的审计绕过漏洞。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0579"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:40.243","remediation":"在 Windows NT 中打开注册表编辑器 regedt32，进入\"安全\"→\"审核\"，为 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SYSTEM、SOFTWARE 等非关键注册表项添加\"成功\"与\"失败\"的审核项；同时运行 regedt32 中\"选项\"→\"审核\"确保已启用注册表审核策略。将域控制器与重要服务器加入域安全策略强制开启审计，并定期审阅安全日志，无法立即配置时限制远程注册表访问（禁用 Remote Registry 服务）作为缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/228","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/770e8f09ce14e637a09c7c619e10772aa6172bea/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0579.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0579","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0579.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/e1298ff7aafe81b936ca67ecef34c3124d6c72f0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0579.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2a2be81fd4b47dc35d815a995b6429bd116a3b84/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-fvqx-8235-38mw/GHSA-fvqx-8235-38mw.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0579.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86238/info.html","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000442.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/zephyros1603/RadiantProcessors/blob/7d44cb1cd4b9e088fbe463f1b19be50a04c2efe8/Backend/RAG/data/allitems.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0845.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0843","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0843.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0577","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9105,\"outputTokens\":17,\"totalTokens\":10786}}","description":"Windows NT 系统的文件审计策略存在安全配置缺陷，对于非关键文件或目录，系统不会记录访问成功或失败的事件日志。攻击者在已获得目标系统访问权限的情况下，可借此对敏感但被标记为\"非关键\"的文件或目录进行未授权读取、修改或删除操作，而其行为不会触发任何审计告警，从而规避安全监控与事后溯源。该漏洞影响启用了文件审计策略但未正确配置关键路径的 Windows NT 系统，CVSS 评分达 10.0，危害等级极为严重。利用方式主要为本地或低权限攻击者通过操纵审计策略绕过日志监控实施隐蔽攻击，修复建议是正确配置审计策略，将重要文件与目录纳入审计范围并启用成功与失败事件的双重记录。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0577"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:40.007","remediation":"在 Windows NT 的「本地安全策略」→「审核策略」中启用「审核对象访问」的成功和失败审核，然后对关键目录（如系统目录、敏感数据目录）应用审核条目，在 ACL 高级设置中添加 Everyone 组的「完全控制」审核。对于 Windows 2000 及以上版本，建议升级操作系统以获取更完善的审核功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0577","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/770e8f09ce14e637a09c7c619e10772aa6172bea/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0577.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0577","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0577.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/e1298ff7aafe81b936ca67ecef34c3124d6c72f0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0577.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2a2be81fd4b47dc35d815a995b6429bd116a3b84/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-p3j3-4263-vqh3/GHSA-p3j3-4263-vqh3.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0577.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86044/info.html","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000440.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--d07355ed-bbf5-4784-ac55-957a53c7d6f5.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0843.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0836","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0836.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0571","title":"ZyXEL Prestige 路由器 管理接口未授权访问漏洞","description":"这是一个影响 ZyXEL Prestige 路由器的管理和配置服务漏洞。该路由的管理界面（包括 Web 管理界面或 Telnet 服务）配置不当，允许来自任意网络的未授权连接。攻击者无需身份验证即可访问路由器的管理服务，能够进行配置修改、查看网络状态或执行其他管理操作，从而可能导致路由设备被完全控制，网络安全架构被破坏，甚至成为进一步攻击的跳板。此类漏洞影响于支持远程管理的网络设备，攻击者可通过网络直接对路由进行非法操作，危害网络基础设施安全。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0571"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:39.527","remediation":"升级 ZyXEL Prestige 路由器固件至最新版本，建议开启访问控制列表 (ACL) 仅允许特定 IP 访问管理接口，并关闭不必要的服务如 Telnet，使用强密码并启用 HTTPS 管理。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0571","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/abfccbe3a11aa2b9dde2cfba5a12ba6256820a51/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0571.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0571","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0571.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/ed6bb242e8dd7e27b54cbf189349b0ad2ae7c304/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0571.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/zyxel_pwd.nasl","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/780ea229276a503f17a45c7ccc9fc5e26e6b2447/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-c7jg-hmf3-2v5x/GHSA-c7jg-hmf3-2v5x.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0571.json","https://github.com/LubyRuffy/plugins/blob/f873b19f27c95eaf2993ca4acde5cb7965d2ee3f/pre2008/zyxel_http_pwd.nasl","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0836.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0835","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0835.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0570","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":16244,\"outputTokens\":31,\"totalTokens\":16275}}","description":"Windows NT 操作系统未启用密码过滤器实用程序（如 PASSFILT.DLL），导致系统未对账户密码的强度与复杂度进行强制校验。该漏洞影响所有未配置密码过滤器的 Windows NT 域控制器与成员服务器，攻击条件为本地或远程获得账户创建/修改权限的攻击者。利用方式为攻击者可为账户设置弱口令、空口令或字典易猜密码，从而绕过密码策略并提升暴力破解与未授权登录的成功率，严重威胁系统身份安全。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0570"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:39.403","remediation":"为 Windows NT 安装并启用密码过滤实用程序（如微软 PASSFILT.DLL），将其配置到系统密码策略中强制复杂密码；通过「管理工具→域用户管理器→策略→密码策略」勾选\"密码必须符合复杂性要求\"并应用。同时启用账户锁定策略，限制口令尝试次数，并以最小权限原则限制可修改账户策略的用户，作为缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0570","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/abfccbe3a11aa2b9dde2cfba5a12ba6256820a51/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0570.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0570","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0570.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/ed6bb242e8dd7e27b54cbf189349b0ad2ae7c304/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0570.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/780ea229276a503f17a45c7ccc9fc5e26e6b2447/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9jjm-6ch3-q532/GHSA-9jjm-6ch3-q532.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0570.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/zephyros1603/RadiantProcessors/blob/7d44cb1cd4b9e088fbe463f1b19be50a04c2efe8/Backend/RAG/data/allitems.txt","https://github.com/VulnerabilityHistoryProject/mega-foss/blob/4829eeb7b0101570abbc87d2a697f2c0c2f4e5c3/src/cve/graphql/trial.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0570.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0835.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0831","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0831.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0568","title":"Sun Solaris rpc.admind 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Solaris rpc.admind 守护进程未以安全模式运行，导致远程攻击者可利用 RPC 服务的配置缺陷绕过权限控制，在未经身份认证的情况下执行任意代码或获取系统敏感信息。该漏洞影响运行 rpc.admind 服务的 Solaris 2.x/7/8 等版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，属于严重级别。攻击者仅需向目标主机发送特制的 RPC 请求即可触发漏洞，无需用户交互，利用门槛极低。Sun Microsystems 已发布补丁修复此问题，建议升级至修复版本或禁用不必要的 RPC 服务。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0568"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:39.160","remediation":"升级到 Solaris 2.6 最新补丁簇或 Solaris 7 及以上版本，并安装 Sun 官方安全补丁（如 105396 系列）。同时修改 /etc/inetd.conf，将 rpc.admind 配置为以安全模式运行（添加 -s 参数），或通过防火墙限制 100232 端口仅允许可信内网访问，禁用不必要的 RPC 服务以缓解风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0568","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/abfccbe3a11aa2b9dde2cfba5a12ba6256820a51/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0568.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0568","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0568.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/ed6bb242e8dd7e27b54cbf189349b0ad2ae7c304/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0568.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/780ea229276a503f17a45c7ccc9fc5e26e6b2447/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5pmv-f82w-3v96/GHSA-5pmv-f82w-3v96.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0568.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/zephyros1603/RadiantProcessors/blob/7d44cb1cd4b9e088fbe463f1b19be50a04c2efe8/Backend/RAG/data/allitems.txt","https://github.com/VulnerabilityHistoryProject/mega-foss/blob/4829eeb7b0101570abbc87d2a697f2c0c2f4e5c3/src/cve/graphql/trial.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0568.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0831.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0828","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0828.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0565","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":10368,\"inputTokens\":407,\"outputTokens\":17,\"totalTokens\":10792}}","description":"Sendmail 邮件传输代理存在别名配置漏洞，攻击者可通过构造包含管道符（|）的别名文件条目，将邮件输入直接传递给任意系统命令执行。该漏洞影响早期版本的 Sendmail 系统，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可在运行 Sendmail 的服务器上执行任意命令，获得服务器控制权。攻击者需能够向 Sendmail 别名文件写入或修改内容，进而通过邮件投递触发命令执行，最终可能导致系统被完全入侵，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0565"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:38.933","remediation":"升级 Sendmail 到 8.9.3 或更高版本以修复别名管道执行漏洞。如无法立即升级，应在 sendmail.cf 中设置 DontBlameSendmail=no 或删除 /etc/aliases 中所有含管道符 \"|\" 的别名条目，并将 alias 文件权限设为只有 root 可读写（chmod 644 /etc/aliases），同时使用 /etc/sendmail.cw 限制中继域名，减少攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0565","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0565.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/abfccbe3a11aa2b9dde2cfba5a12ba6256820a51/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0565.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0565","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2a20296d4b03dbd5c5991115b8296a9f2b947592/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0565.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0565.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/780ea229276a503f17a45c7ccc9fc5e26e6b2447/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6pqr-5mv4-2r65/GHSA-6pqr-5mv4-2r65.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0565.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86048/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0828.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0827","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0827.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0564","title":"开源打印机远程安全漏洞","description":"OpenSource Printer 存在未授权访问漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过发送特制的打印任务强制目标打印机输出任意文档，或导致打印机进入瘫痪状态无法正常使用。该漏洞主要影响未设置访问密码的打印机，攻击者通过网络直接访问打印服务即可发起攻击，造成敏感信息泄露、纸张浪费或拒绝服务等后果。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0564"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:38.820","remediation":"在打印机的管理界面中启用密码认证功能，配置强密码并限制仅授权用户可以提交打印任务；同时通过防火墙或网络访问控制列表（ACL）仅允许受信任的 IP 地址访问打印机端口，阻止外部未授权访问。建议升级到支持认证机制的最新固件版本，并在无法立即升级时暂时禁用远程打印功能，仅允许本地打印以降低风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0564","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/abfccbe3a11aa2b9dde2cfba5a12ba6256820a51/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0564.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0564","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0564.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2a20296d4b03dbd5c5991115b8296a9f2b947592/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0564.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/780ea229276a503f17a45c7ccc9fc5e26e6b2447/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3qxq-4rfh-fpmx/GHSA-3qxq-4rfh-fpmx.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0564.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86054/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--de6026d9-734b-4b8f-9806-be65b8ba58d6.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0827.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0822","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0822.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0561","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9114,\"outputTokens\":20,\"totalTokens\":10798}}","description":"Microsoft IIS 服务器默认启用了服务器端包含（SSI）文件中的 #exec 指令功能。该漏洞原理在于 Web 服务器在处理 .shtml 等 SSI 页面时，允许攻击者通过构造包含 `<!--#exec cmd=\"...\" -->` 的页面或请求，在服务端执行任意系统命令。受影响范围为开启了 SSI 且未禁用 #exec 的 Microsoft IIS 版本（如 IIS 4.0/5.0 早期默认配置）。攻击条件为：目标站点允许上传或托管 SSI 文件、或存在可被用户控制的 SSI 解析路径，且攻击者能够向服务器提交包含恶意 #exec 指令的请求。利用方式为：攻击者将含 #exec 指令的 SSI 内容提交至目标，诱导服务器解析执行，从而在主机上以 Web 服务账户权限运行命令，可能导致信息泄露、权限提升或进一步入侵。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0561"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:38.580","remediation":"在 IIS 管理器的网站属性中禁用 Server Side Include (SSI) 执行权限，或通过修改 MetaBase.xml 将 SSIEnable 设为 False。若必须使用 SSI，应删除所有 .stm/.shtml 文件中的 #exec 和 #include 指令，并在 Internet 服务管理器中将这些扩展名映射到静态文件处理器而非 ssinc.dll，同时升级到 IIS 6.0 及以上版本以获得更严格的安全默认配置。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0561","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0561.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/abfccbe3a11aa2b9dde2cfba5a12ba6256820a51/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0561.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0561","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2a20296d4b03dbd5c5991115b8296a9f2b947592/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0561.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0561.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/780ea229276a503f17a45c7ccc9fc5e26e6b2447/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-56f4-vjr2-wrvq/GHSA-56f4-vjr2-wrvq.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0561.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86059/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0822.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0822.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0818","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0818.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0556","title":"Unix 操作系统 重复 UID 权限提升漏洞","description":"Unix系统中的账户UID重复漏洞是指系统中两个或多个用户账户被分配了相同的用户标识符，这违反了Unix/Linux系统中账户必须拥有唯一UID的基本安全原则。该漏洞导致系统无法准确区分不同用户的身份访问权限，攻击者可通过创建与特权账户相同的UID来冒充授权用户，访问敏感文件、提升权限并绕过访问控制。漏洞影响范围涵盖所有使用Unix系统的服务器和工作站，只要存在账户重复现象即可触发，攻击条件相对简单，只需要对目标进行账户操作即可。此外，由于UID重复导致文件权限混乱，攻击者还能读取或修改属于其他用户的机密数据，造成严重的权限混淆和安全隐患。漏洞的 CVSS 评分高达 10（满分），表明其安全危害极其严重。这种漏洞通常存在于配置混乱、未严格实施账户管理的Unix系统中，补丁措施包括严格执行账户唯一性检查和使用自动化账户管理工具。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0556"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:38.230","remediation":"检查 /etc/passwd 中所有用户 UID，确保每个用户拥有唯一 UID。使用 `awk -F: '{print $3}' /etc/passwd | sort | uniq -d` 查找重复 UID，对冲突账户使用 `usermod -u <新UID>` 分配独立 UID，并同步更新该用户所属文件的 UID（`find / -user <旧UID> -exec chown <新UID> {} +`）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/876","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/476c79e4154073134b6998fc7a1fcba149340485/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0556.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0556","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0556.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/3950bef6f70c411ea08c8b2f1665dbd7d38277bd/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0556.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/780ea229276a503f17a45c7ccc9fc5e26e6b2447/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-573h-p65m-cffp/GHSA-573h-p65m-cffp.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0556.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/zephyros1603/RadiantProcessors/blob/7d44cb1cd4b9e088fbe463f1b19be50a04c2efe8/Backend/RAG/data/allitems.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0556.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0818.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0818.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0817","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0817.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0555","title":"Unix系统 非 root 账户 UID 0 权限提升漏洞","description":"Unix 系统中存在权限配置不当漏洞：某个非 root 名称的账户被错误地分配了 UID 0（即 root 用户标识符）。由于操作系统以 UID 而非用户名为依据判定特权，该账户因此拥有与 root 等同的超级用户权限。影响范围涵盖所有采用传统 UID 权限模型的 Unix 及类 Unix 系统。攻击条件为攻击者已获得该异常账户凭据或利用其他途径登录该账户。利用方式上，攻击者可直接以该账户执行任意系统管理操作（如读取/修改敏感文件、创建后门、提权持久化），等效于完全控制整台主机，危害等级严重（CVSS 10.0）。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0555"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:38.127","remediation":"立即在系统中检查所有用户账户的UID分配，删除所有不应该拥有UID 0的非root账户，并重新创建root账户以彻底恢复系统权限控制机制。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0555","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/476c79e4154073134b6998fc7a1fcba149340485/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0555.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0555","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0555.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/3950bef6f70c411ea08c8b2f1665dbd7d38277bd/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0555.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/780ea229276a503f17a45c7ccc9fc5e26e6b2447/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-68gv-9r74-xmm7/GHSA-68gv-9r74-xmm7.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0555.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86050/info.html","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--6aea9a46-be07-4e3a-9755-ac4aac4c4ebb.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/zephyros1603/RadiantProcessors/blob/7d44cb1cd4b9e088fbe463f1b19be50a04c2efe8/Backend/RAG/data/allitems.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0817.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0813","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0813.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0549","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 自动以管理员身份登录后无需认证访问漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统在配置启用自动登录（AutoAdminLogon）功能后，会在系统重启时自动以管理员或指定用户身份登录，且登录凭据以明文形式存储于注册表 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows NT\\CurrentVersion\\Winlogon 的 DefaultPassword 项中。攻击者在能够物理接触设备或获取注册表读取权限的情况下，可直接提取明文口令并获得系统级访问权限，无需任何认证即可完全控制主机。该配置缺陷使得本地安全边界失效，影响所有启用了自动登录的 Windows NT 工作站与服务器。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0549"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","remediation":"禁用 Windows NT 自动登录：运行 regedit，进入 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows NT\\CurrentVersion\\Winlogon，将 AutoAdminLogon 设为 0，并删除 DefaultPassword、DefaultUserName、DefaultDomainName 中的明文凭据；为管理员账户设置强口令，或通过组策略/域控强制交互式登录。建议升级至 Windows 2000 及后续版本以规避该配置风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0549","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/476c79e4154073134b6998fc7a1fcba149340485/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0549.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0549.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/780ea229276a503f17a45c7ccc9fc5e26e6b2447/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-w9wr-9v9x-q549/GHSA-w9wr-9v9x-q549.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0813.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0805","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0805.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0539","title":"Unix 主机信任关系未授权访问漏洞","description":"CVE-1999-0539 涉及两台 Unix 主机之间建立的信任关系（如基于 .rhosts 或 hosts.equiv 的配置）。其原理是系统允许受信任的主机在无需身份认证的情况下以特定用户身份登录或执行命令。影响范围为配置了主机间信任关系的 Unix 系统，攻击者只要能够控制其中一台受信任主机，或以伪造源地址等方式冒用信任主机身份，即可在目标主机上绕过密码验证直接访问资源或执行命令，从而扩大攻击面并可能导致未授权访问与权限提升。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0539"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:36.267","remediation":"删除或清空各主机的 .rhosts 文件及 /etc/hosts.equiv 文件中的信任条目，确保仅允许明确授权的主机建立信任关系；禁用 rlogin、rsh、rcp 等基于信任机制的传统远程服务，改用 SSH 密钥认证方式替代；在防火墙或网络层面限制 rlogin/rcp 相关端口（513、514）的访问，仅允许必要的管理主机通过 SSH 访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/723","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/442e3d0f3c777e02c70fc200a453fe1f1f8a2431/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0539.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0539","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0539.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/19ba23eb6f8fe22cdd9a46164160f96a7cf3fffd/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0539.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/51a0e15452743e596ced46bb3f156961c52df5bb/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7v5h-pgc3-6pcp/GHSA-7v5h-pgc3-6pcp.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0539.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/zephyros1603/RadiantProcessors/blob/7d44cb1cd4b9e088fbe463f1b19be50a04c2efe8/Backend/RAG/data/allitems.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0539.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0805.toml"}]